race.comment: STEP ASIDE (12) deserves his shot at this level and this looks a target race fourth-up. Sat midfield and wide with a respectable fourth over this track and trip. Key jockey change on the limit and looks the value play. SANDPAPER (1) set a blistering tempo early and was left a sitting shot late, when sixth over 1400m in the Buffering at Eagle Farm. Will roll forward again and give plenty of cheek. THUNDERLIPS (10) should relish the good tempo and look for him launching late. Strips fitter third-up and will appreciate reuniting with Gibbons. FIRE STAR (7) bounced back sharply last time at Eagle Farm when beaten a head. Kept fresh with a month between, keeping the legs ticking over with a stylish trial win here. Can give this a shake.
